gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 143, Wizards 120
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Wizards, 143-120 tonight in Indiana. Bruce Brown led the Pacers with 24 points (6-8 3PT FG) as Tyrese Haliburton totaled 20 points and 11 assists for the Pacers, who shot 20-43 from beyond the arc overall. Kyle Kuzma led the Wizards with 25 points while Jordan Poole added 18 points and five assists.
